{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "391aaf6f-19f3-4157-ba47-063012294360",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 1 02 Second Class",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "9dff20d4-9833-432f-9650-c14864d65724",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "0e1a0452-20dc-47ff-a526-3bea43525a68",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "bddf24ee-8f7f-44c4-bf17-662dd2a53347",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For today's lesson, we will discuss Magic, Mojo, and Wizards. All living creatures have some essence of magic within them. It's the very spark of life.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "730c928c-c84b-489a-a1b8-d1204b71fb42",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Magic is the potential to tap into the energy within oneself as well as the power that surrounds us. This energy is known as Mana or, as we call it in the Magic for Mundanes class, Mojo.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "3f85e25f-2506-4cbd-9b0a-cb174ee11b4a",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Magic can be used in many different ways. True Wizardry is a method of shaping Magick through the use of symbols or runes. The Wizard visualizes the rune and then channels the Mojo to cast spells. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "abd5e4ee-c173-4272-9543-a60be7df612d",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "You all have some minor magical abilities that we will develop to their greatest degree through this class. While you'll never be true Wizards, you can become perfectly adequate Magic-Users.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1e8b9afb-1b1c-4e8e-ace6-565798b0f350",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Before I go into greater detail, are there any questions about Magick, Mojo, or Wizardry?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "9436041f-4355-4993-a588-8a6c17f7b973",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "50ec17d7-3a55-4f5e-bea7-91dc4351d486",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "112e16ca-b087-4079-adea-000ff18bddbd",
                            "text": "Compliment the Professor on Her Explanations",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "277a5e76-98ca-469d-b6aa-16b86a571565",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Since you've explained everything so well, I think we all get what you are talking about.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "614151cd-75ae-47a5-8a71-9009fab0a0e7",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That's so good to know. I sometimes get rather carried away by this subject since Magick is so dear to my heart. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "6cbfe695-8ca2-4c4a-a223-e20bcb3631b2",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "26",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "5d0523cd-f8f5-4234-8569-08bfde9e7575",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": false
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "8b42e236-9c60-4901-82f7-d2720c9374f3",
                            "text": "Ask the Difference Between Magick and Magic",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0e794a79-2770-4723-b020-48d41b747cdb",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Is there a difference between Magic and <i>Magick</i>?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "85c1792a-0653-4b93-af2b-d8b985a45fd7",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Indeed there is, Mr. O'Conner. <i>Magic</i> is the supernatural potential that allows one to use Mojo to manipulate reality. <i>Magick</i> is the actual usage of such potential. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "43449419-03d3-498a-9d45-0edfb32f16cd",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "You have the Magic skill. It is only when you use the Magic skill that you create Magick. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a06948b6-c4d7-4240-8111-d408887ddafd",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "While I'm sure this is as clear to you as Shapeirian coffee, fear not. After tomorrow's class, you will be wielding your own Magick.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "72a67939-a638-4a3f-8443-889a312b2cac",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "26",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "e77ca280-652f-48f7-9173-fb9bbf691bed",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": false
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "5c035324-4cab-4f25-adeb-3dc54e01d5d7",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "683869a8-717c-4f41-83af-1f76c655e443",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "So do you find it beneath you to have to teach mundanes like us with so little magic? Maybe you should have called this class <i>Magic for Dummies</i>.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "8cd179b5-3eff-4f12-9a96-1ab0f6334374",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "26",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "c24a5e50-d1aa-4714-aff8-843c8c9e11a6",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "8ae1fe5c-3dc3-4f2d-9215-1b99f218ce38",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "1",
                                                "change": "0",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c18b362f-db60-4360-a247-06648bf7744c",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I would never insult your intelligence like that! I am sure that most of you are quite clever in your own way. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d683b000-1697-410f-a8d1-c03425d37694",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It gives me a great deal of satisfaction to teach this class. I enjoy this opportunity to help awaken your magical potential and share with you all the joy of Magick.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "5b36803f-5af8-46b9-b4d7-f2979bd46fc4",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "aeae24b0-2a31-4f6a-a999-c873eb1993ef",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Let us finish our tea and then we will delve deeper into the differences between Magic-Users and Wizards...",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
